    12| * Hard enforcement (no claims without real commands):
    13| *   - No files changed      → "NO CODE CHANGED — no development was completed."
    14| *   - No tests run          → "NOT VERIFIED — tests were not run."
    15| *   - Patch could not write  → "BLOCKED — I do not have code write access."
